text.section:
The plan of merger shall set forth:
The name of each partnership or limited partnership that is a party to the merger;
The name of the surviving entity into which the other partnerships or limited partnerships will merge;
Whether the surviving entity is a partnership or a limited partnership and the status of each partner;
The terms and conditions of the merger;
The manner and basis of converting the interests of each party to the merger into interests or obligations of the surviving entity, or into money or other property in whole or part; and
The street address of the surviving entity's chief executive office.
